To build this project you will need 

   1. nlohmann json.
   2. libfmt.
   3. boost > 1.71.
   4. libsodium.
   5. openssl.

On debian systems 1. and 2. and 4. can be installed from packages

   $ sudo apt-get install nlohmann-json3-dev
   $ sudo apt-get install libfmt3-dev
   $ sudo apt-get install libsodium-dev
   $ sudo apt-get install libssl-dev

Occase makes direct use of only three boost packages
  
  1. Asio
  2. Beast
  3. Program Options

To build occase there is not need to build boost whole, for example

   $ ./bootstrap.sh --with-libraries=program_options,system --prefix=/opt/boost_1_71_0/
   $ ./b2
   $ sudo b2 install

The Makefile assumes boost is installed in

   boost_inc_dir = /opt/boost_1_71_0/include
   boost_lib_dir = /opt/boost_1_71_0/lib

Change that if needed.

